Opened Rviz in a new terminal using these three steps:

source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash
source ~/arctos_ws/devel/setup.bash
roslaunch arctos_config demo.launch


Opened a new terminal
source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash
source ~/arctos_ws/devel/setup.bash
cd ~/arctos_ws/src/arctos_scripts/scripts
All three files are located in this folder. The one that works is the make_9_points

Every time a new change is made, did the following to make the file executable: chmod +x name_of_file.py

In same terminal, in scripts directory, did the following:
rosrun arctos_scripts make_9_points.py
